<Paragraph Margin="0,0" FontSize="12" Foreground="silver">Signs are great. As we discussed at length in our Taking Inventory article on signs a few years ago, theyâ€™re the perfect way to label your storage, leave yourself reminders, and to stop yourself getting lost.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph Margin="0,0" FontSize="12" Foreground="silver">But sometimes you want something a bit fancier, something thatâ€™s more of an advertisement than a mere label. Thatâ€™s why, in the Trails & Tales update in June 2023, we added a far more impressive alternative. Behold! Hanging signs! Our item of the month!</Paragraph>
